            <p><add hand="#barker">Character certificate of Hardy Coward.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>George Poindexter, Governor of the <placeName>State of Mississippi</placeName>.</persName></p>

<p><hi rend="italic">To all to whom these presents shall come:</hi></p>

<p>Know ye, That Whereas it is represented to me, that <persName>Hardy
Coward</persName>, a Citizen of the <placeName>County of Amite</placeName>, and State aforesaid, is
desirous of travelling into the <placeName>Province of Texas</placeName>, on his own private<pb n="426"/>
business; I do therefore, make known to all persons whom it may
concern, that the said <persName>Hardy Coward</persName> is a man of family, and of
good character and conduct; and I desire that he may be received
accordingly.</p>

<p>Given under my hand and the Great Seal of said State, at 
<placeName>Columbia</placeName>, the <date when="1821-11-09">ninth day of November, A. D. 1821</date></p>

<p><persName>Geo Poindexter</persName></p>

        </div1>
